{"id": "art-115", "label": "Art. 115", "title": "Art. 115", "slug": "art-115", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 115 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1294262389\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2329\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1294262389\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Pentru validitatea deliber&#259;rilor adun&#259;rii\ngenerale extraordinare este necesar&#259; la prima convocare <span\nclass=SpellE>prezen&#355;a</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inând</span> cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o\np&#259;trime din num&#259;rul total de drepturi de vot, iar la convoc&#259;rile\nurm&#259;toare, <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;a</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nreprezentând cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o cincime din\nnum&#259;rul total de drepturi de vot.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1406690500\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2328\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1406690500\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Hot&#259;rârile sunt luate cu majoritatea voturilor <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span> de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span> sau <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>.\nDecizia de modificare a obiectului principal de activitate al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, de reducere sau majorare a\ncapitalului social, de schimbare a formei juridice, de fuziune, divizare sau de\ndizolvare a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> se ia cu o\nmajoritate de cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> dou&#259; treimi din\ndrepturile de vot <span class=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span> sau\n<span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_931231764\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2327\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_931231764\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În actul constitutiv se pot stipula <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;e</span>\nde cvorum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de majoritate mai mari.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}